">value</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Input Button\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"e-btn e-link\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>a ID<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"anchorbtn\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"e-btn e-primary\"</span> href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Google<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>a<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div</code></pre></div>","id":"9a66972e-6a98-5b0f-bbd1-1f321fd69c25","fields":{"slug":"/button/how-to/customize-input-and-anchor-elements/","parentPath":"button/how-to","childPath":"customize-input-and-anchor-elements","gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"Button/How To/Customize input and anchor elements","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"How to Customize input and anchor elements in Blazor [Preview] Button component - Syncfusion","description":"Checkout and learn about Customize input and anchor elements in Blazor [Preview] Button component of Syncfusion Essential JS 2, and more details.","platform":"Blazor [Preview]","isRobots":true}},"gcse":"014729256687841406486:qzbiyd0sri4","header":"","breadCrumb":"Button/How To/Create a Block Button","isReleaseNotes":false,"title":"How to Create a Block Button in Blazor [Preview] Button component - Syncfusion","descr